==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reland
<hw>Re*land"</hw> <pr>(r?-l?nd")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To land
again; to put on land, as that which had been shipped or
embarked.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reland</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Reland
<hw>Re*land"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To go on shore after having
embarked; to land again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Relapse</ent>⟦br⟧
